      "title": "Troops arrest duo with 10.4 kg of ICE worth Rs. 150mn in Mannar",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two men were arrested by the Army with 10.4 kg of ICE (methamphetamine crystals) which has a street value of more than Rs. 150 million at a Mannar roadblock this morning.",
        "Army said the two men were attempting to shuttle those drugs from Thalaimannar to Vangalai area in a cab.",
        "Army troopers handed over those suspects and the seized drugs to the Mannar Police station for further inquiries. (Darshana Sanjeewa Balasuriya)"
      ],
